					"value": "Scyre, Mortach of Kelemvor, has been told that a little girl is practicing Necromancy in the graveyard. This is when you catch up to them both, and you get one last chance to intervene. In this dialogue you can encourage Nina to stop her Necromancy, threaten her, or even convince her to try again later."
